<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('../partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

  <main id="main-content">
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center gy-4">
          <div class="col-lg-8">
            <h1>Mark Ashkenazi</h1>
            <h2 class=""hero-role>Test Automation Engineer | Accessibility Advocate</h2>
            <p class="lead hero-lead">
              This portfolio documents software projects, testing artefacts, accessibility-focused work, and practical development evidence from university, capstone, and software testing training.
            </p>

            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
              <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/projects">View projects</a>
              <a class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg" href="/testing">View testing artefacts</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">Portfolio structure</p>
          <h2>What this site will show</h2>
          <p>
            The site is being built around evidence rather than claims: project work, testing documentation, accessibility defects, and implementation notes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <article class="info-card h-100">
              <h3>Development projects</h3>
              <p>
                University and capstone projects showing application structure, user interface work, persistence, mobile features, and delivery context.
              </p>
              <a href="/projects">Browse projects</a>
            </article>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-4">
            <article class="info-card h-100">
              <h3>Testing artefacts</h3>
              <p>
                Test scenarios, test cases, defect reports, API testing, performance testing, UI automation, SQL checks, and screenshots.
              </p>
              <a href="/testing">Browse testing work</a>
            </article>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-4">
            <article class="info-card h-100">
              <h3>Accessibility focus</h3>
              <p>
                WCAG-based defect examples, accessibility scan evidence, remediation thinking, and governance-focused project documentation.
              </p>
              <a href="/accessibility">Browse accessibility work</a>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>